{"word":"θεωρέω","slug":"θεωρέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ϑεωρέω</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <el>ϑεωρός</el> ‘spectator’]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘pay attention to’, <b>look at, observe, watch, behold <a href='B:470 27:55'>Mt 27:55</a>; <a href='B:480 12:41'>Mk 12:41</a>; <a href='B:490 14:29'>Lk 14:29</a>; <a href='B:490 21:6'>21:6</a>; <a href='B:500 20:6'>J 20:6</a>, <a href='B:500 20:12'>12</a>; <a href='B:510 7:56'>Ac 7:56</a>; <a href='B:510 9:7'>9:7</a>; <a href='B:510 17:16'>17:16</a>. Catch sight of, take notice of <a href='B:480 3:11'>Mk 3:11</a>.</b> In apparent wordplay <b><a href='B:500 12:45'>J 12:45a</a></b> (for <b>45b</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ s.\">s.</a> 2 below). <b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘conclude on the basis of personal experience’, <b>infer, see <a href='B:500 4:19'>J 4:19</a>; <a href='B:500 12:19'>12:19</a>, <a href='B:500 12:45'>45b</a></b> (<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ s.\">s.</a> 1 above); <b><a href='B:500 16:19'>16:19</a>; <a href='B:510 4:13'>Ac 4:13</a>; <a href='B:510 17:22'>17:22</a>; <a href='B:650 7:4'>Hb 7:4</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>3.</pp></b> ‘have awareness in depth’ <b>perceive <a href='B:500 14:17'>J 14:17</a>; <a href='B:500 17:24'>17:24</a>; experience <a href='B:500 8:51'>8:51</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:Θευδᾶς\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:θεωρία\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}